[
  {
    "startTime": 4.9,
    "endTime": 4.923,
    "text": "- How can you hate"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.923,
    "endTime": 6.52,
    "text": "assigned seating at the movie theater?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.52,
    "endTime": 8.45,
    "text": "- Because sometimes one of the rows is full of teens"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.45,
    "endTime": 9.574,
    "text": "and, I don't know just looking at the screen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.574,
    "endTime": 11.86,
    "text": "- But you can see where the groups are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.86,
    "endTime": 12.7,
    "text": "when you look at the screen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.7,
    "endTime": 14.799999999999999,
    "text": "- Right, and sometimes I have to sit next to a group anyway."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.801,
    "endTime": 17.7,
    "text": "I don't like assigned seating in a movie theater."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.7,
    "endTime": 17.99,
    "text": "- But why not?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.99,
    "endTime": 18.97,
    "text": "You have to like this!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.97,
    "endTime": 19.93,
    "text": "It's driving me crazy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.93,
    "endTime": 20.762,
    "text": "- I like what I like."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.763,
    "endTime": 21.596,
    "text": "- Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.596,
    "endTime": 24.240000000000002,
    "text": "I think, we can all agree this conversation sucks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.24,
    "endTime": 25.799999999999997,
    "text": "- But listen, Rega,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.8,
    "endTime": 26.134,
    "text": "isn't it how wrong is? - Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.135,
    "endTime": 27.1,
    "text": "Who wants ice cream?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.1,
    "endTime": 30.743000000000002,
    "text": "- Nah, I'm not really that into ice cream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.637,
    "endTime": 32.47,
    "text": "- What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.47,
    "endTime": 35.25,
